name: Cycling Posters
description:
Ride OTR
Two-color, 18" x 24"
Hand-pulled silkscreen poster featuring an OTR pennyfarthing and line illustrations of OTR landmarks.


An Ode to Bicycles Letterpress Poster — STILL $25
Two-color, 18" x 24"
To celebrate my love of bicycles I wrote some short prose and typeset it in antique wood type with hand-carved two linoleum block illustrations.


USA Pro Challenge 2012: Colorado Springs — ONLY $10!
Full-color, 18" x 24"
The peloton rides serenely through the Garden of the Gods under the impressive Pikes Peak.


Picnic in the Mud
Three-color, 9" x 24"
A poster celebrating cyclocross roots in farm fields, mud, picnics and parasols.


Belgian Waffle
Full-color, 18" x 24"
A poster created for the Kings Cyclocross International—where reigning Belgian World Champ Niels Albert won in style.
